  "keyFeatures": [
    "Three model sizes: E1-150m, E1-300m, E1-600m (HuggingFace-hosted)",
    "Single-sequence protein encoding with masked language modeling",
    "Retrieval-augmented inference using homologous sequences (MSA context)",
    "Per-residue logits and embeddings output",
    "Zero-shot fitness prediction for protein variants",
    "In-silico site saturation mutagenesis via masked-marginal scoring",
    "Flash attention support for Ampere and newer GPUs (BF16 precision)",
    "KV-cache for efficient retrieval-augmented prediction",
    "Drop-in replacement for ESM family of models",
    "Distributed inference support via PyTorch distributed"
  ],
